<span class="header1">Outdoor paired with Technology (AF)</span>

<p>With an "AF" interest, you will want to combine your interest in open-air occupations with your interest in technologies. You like to conduct research, employ change and apply what you know,  to work settings of the technologies and outdoors.</p>
<p>Many of the occupations in this pairing require that you have specialized and/or technical training after high school. Many require college degrees or college level courses.</p>

